漢米爾頓在[[2010年中國大獎賽|中國]]落後简森·巴顿以第2名完賽，為麥拉倫達成繼[[2007年意大利大奖赛|2007年意大利大奖赛]]後的首次一、二名完賽。<ref name="Autosport race">{{cite journal|last=Hughes|first=Mark|date=2010-04-22|title=McLaren's gang of two rules China|journal=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|volume=200|issue=4|pages=26–37}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2010/04/19/points-for-petrov-and-first-mclaren-1-2-since-2007-chinese-gp-stats-and-facts/ |title=Points for Petrov and first McLaren 1-2 since 2007 (Chinese GP stats and facts) |date=2010-04-19 |first=Keith |last=Collantine |work=f1fanatic.co.uk |publisher=F1 Fanatic |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2017-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170426185354/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2010/04/19/points-for-petrov-and-first-mclaren-1-2-since-2007-chinese-gp-stats-and-facts/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>漢米爾頓與維泰爾因為在維修道相互爭道，兩人賽後皆受到懲戒。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://en.espn.co.uk/china/motorsport/story/14928.html |title=No penalty for Hamilton or Vettel after pit lane incident |date=2010-04-18 |work=espnf1.com |publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808235746/http://en.espn.co.uk/china/motorsport/story/14928.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在[[2010年西班牙大獎賽|巴塞隆納]]從第3位發車，卻在最後幾圈遭遇鋁圈故障問題，致使他的車輛失控撞上護欄，僅能以退賽收場。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/may/09/mark-webber-spanish-grand-prix |title=Mark Webber wins Spanish grand prix but Hamilton crashes when second |date=2010-05-09 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |publisher=Guardian News and Media |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2019-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915230342/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/may/09/mark-webber-spanish-grand-prix |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/83530|title=Hamilton's wheel rim failure confirmed|date=2010-05-11|work=autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Publications|first=Jamie|last=O'Leary|accessdate=2010-05-30|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303185506/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/83530|dead-url=no}}</ref>漢米爾頓在[[2010年摩纳哥大奖赛|摩納哥大獎賽]]從第5位起跑後，以第5名完賽。到了{{F1 GP|2010|土耳其}}，漢米爾頓贏得2010年賽季首勝，他與隊友巴頓再度以一、二名完賽。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/motorsport/formula_one/8713482.stm |title=Lewis Hamilton wins Turkish GP after Red Bulls collide |date=2010-05-30 |work=BBC Sport |first=Saj |last=Chowdhury |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109023836/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/motorsport/formula_one/8713482.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>漢米爾頓於{{F1 GP|2010|加拿大}}排位賽中取得桿位，延續他在[[吉爾維倫紐夫賽道|吉爾維倫紐夫賽道]]100%取得桿位的紀錄。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.whtimes.co.uk/sport/f1-hamilton-s-phenomenal-lap-to-take-candian-grand-prix-pole-1-445300 |title=F1: Hamilton’s phenomenal lap to take Candian Grand Prix pole |date=2010-06-13 |work=whtimes.co.uk |first=Alan |last=Davies |publisher=Welwyn Hatfield Times |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2019-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204140148/https://www.whtimes.co.uk/sport/f1-hamilton-s-phenomenal-lap-to-take-candian-grand-prix-pole-1-445300 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在衝線取得桿位後，漢米爾頓的車輛因為燃油不足，車隊下令要求他將車輛停留在賽道上。國際汽聯以其燃料不足採樣標準，且未完成最後繞場將車輛駛回維修站為由懲戒漢米爾頓，同時，車隊也遭罰款一萬美元。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2010/6/10901.html |title=Hamilton storms to Montreal pole |publisher=[[一级方程式赛车|Formula One]] |date=2010-06-12 |accessdate=2010-06-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100614083616/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2010/6/10901.html |archivedate=2010-06-14 }}</ref>儘管如此，漢米爾頓仍舊贏得分站冠軍並登上車手積分榜首位，麥拉倫車隊也達成本季第三次一、二名完賽。到了[[2010年欧洲大奖赛|瓦倫西亞]]，阿隆索透過他的無線電抱怨漢米爾頓非法超越安全車，進而從中得利，致使賽會對漢米爾頓開罰一次限速通過維修道。然而，阿隆索與法拉利車隊對於賽會過晚做出判決感到不滿，使得漢米爾頓執行完罰則後仍然保持在第2名完賽。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/8766250.stm|title=Sebastian Vettel beats Lewis Hamilton in European GP|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2010-06-27|accessdate=2010-08-17}}</ref>漢米爾頓認為阿隆索「酸葡萄心態」，不過，兩人在下一站前達成和解。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.crash.net/f1/news/161344/1/hamilton_everythings_cool_with_alonso_now.html|title=Hamilton: 'Everything's cool' with Alonso now|publisher=crash.net|date=2010-07-07|accessdate=2010-07-08|archive-date=2013-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022044628/http://www.crash.net/f1/news/161344/1/hamilton_everythings_cool_with_alonso_now.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

