Jonathan |last=McEvoy |accessdate=2018-02-13 |location=Monza |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021120120/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-1311322/Fernando-Alonso-storms-victory-Italian-Grand-Prix-Lewis-Hamilton-crashes-opening-lap.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://metro.co.uk/2010/09/26/lewis-hamilton-takes-fury-out-on-steering-wheel-after-singapore-crash-with-mark-webber-530166/ |title=Lewis Hamilton takes fury out on steering wheel after Singapore crash |work=Metro |publisher=Associated Newspapers |date=2010-09-26 |accessdate=2018-02-13 |archive-date=2019-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204123444/https://metro.co.uk/2010/09/26/lewis-hamilton-takes-fury-out-on-steering-wheel-after-singapore-crash-with-mark-webber-530166/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>漢米爾頓在{{F1 GP|2010|日本}}名列第5。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/oct/10/lewis-hamilton-jenson-button-japanese-grand-prix |title=McLaren's Lewis Hamilton has 'worst' weekend at Japanese grand prix |work=The Guardian |publisher=Guardian News and Media |date=2010-10-10 |first=Oliver |last=Owen |accessdate=2018-02-13 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803190303/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/oct/10/lewis-hamilton-jenson-button-japanese-grand-prix |dead-url=no }}</ref>隨後，他在[[2010年韩国大奖赛|韓國]]與[[2010年巴西大獎賽|巴西]]分別取得第2與第4名。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/8085154/F1-Korean-Grand-Prix-Lewis-Hamilton-says-its-back-on-but-we-need-some-luck.html |title=F1 Korean Grand Prix: Lewis Hamilton says 'it's back on but we need some luck' |work=The Telegraph |publisher=Telegraph Media Group |date=2010-10-25 |accessdate=2018-02-13 |archive-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206103221/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/8085154/F1-Korean-Grand-Prix-Lewis-Hamilton-says-its-back-on-but-we-need-some-luck.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-1327465/2010-BRAZILIAN-GRAND-PRIX-LIVE-Follow-drama-unfolds-Interlagos.html |title=LIVE 2010 BRAZILIAN GRAND PRIX: Sebastian Vettel wins in Interlagos as Red Bull clinch constructors' crown |work=Daily Mail |publisher=Associated Newspapers |date=2010-11-07 |first=Philip |last=Duncan |accessdate=2018-02-13 |archive-date=2015-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713181007/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-1327465/2010-BRAZILIAN-GRAND-PRIX-LIVE-Follow-drama-unfolds-Interlagos.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>到了賽季收官站[[2010年阿布扎比大奖赛|阿布達比]]，漢米爾頓以第2名完賽，分站冠軍維泰爾則在本站打破漢米爾頓保有的最年輕一級方程式賽車世界冠軍紀錄。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/nov/14/sebastian-vettel-champion |title=Sebastian Vettel wins Formula One world championship in Abu Dhabi |work=The Guardian |publisher=Guardian News and Media |date=2010-11-14 |accessdate=2018-02-13 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031205440/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/nov/14/sebastian-vettel-champion |dead-url=no }}</ref>

====2011－2012年賽季：效力麥拉倫的最後兩年====
[[File:Lewis_Hamilton_2011_Malaysia_Qualify.jpg|thumb]]
2011年賽季開始前，漢米爾頓譏諷紅牛「只是一家飲料公司」。<ref>{{cite web |last=Weaver |first=Paul |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2011/mar/21/red-bull-lewis-hamilton |title='Red Bull are just a drinks company,' says revved-up Lewis Hamilton |work=The Guardian |date=2011-03-21 |accessdate=2015-07-05 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024313/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2011/mar/21/red-bull-lewis-hamilton |dead-url=no }}</ref>漢米爾頓在賽季開幕站{{F1 GP|2011|澳大利亞}}從第2位起跑，儘管在正賽中因為他的賽車失控衝進緩衝區內，造成車輛底板受損，但是他仍舊以第2名完賽。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9437589.stm|title=Sebastian Vettel beats Lewis Hamilton in Australian GP|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-03-27|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2012-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305115414/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9437589.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>到了{{F1 GP|2011|馬來西亞}}，他再度從第2位起步，不過，卻因輪胎快速惡化所困，以及比賽後段遭法拉利的費爾南多·阿隆索追撞，致使漢米爾頓僅能以第7名完賽。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9453282.stm|title=Sebastian Vettel beats Jenson Button in Malaysian Grand Prix|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-04-10|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2012-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306082831/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9453282.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>賽後，漢米爾頓因為迂迴行駛不正當的防守路徑，遭到判罰20秒加時，名次因而下滑至第8位。<ref>{{cite news|title=Lewis Hamilton and Fernando Alonso hit with penalties|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/formula_one/13029061.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2011-04-10|accessdate=2011-10-15}}</ref>[[2011年中国大奖赛|中國大獎賽]]期間，漢米爾頓從第3位發車取得分站冠軍，中斷維泰爾的跨季四連勝，同時，也成為[[中國大獎賽|中國大獎賽]]自[[2004年中國大獎賽|2004年]]開辦以來，首位在此拿下兩座分站冠軍的車手。<ref>{{cite news|title=Hamilton ends Vettel's winning run as McLaren star takes victory in Chinese Grand Prix|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-1377757/Lewis-Hamilton-wins-Chinese-Grand-Prix.html|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=2011-10-15|location=London|date=2011-04-17|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026193706/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-1377757/Lewis-Hamilton-wins-Chinese-Grand-Prix.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>接下來，漢米爾頓分別在[[2011年土耳其大奖赛|土耳其]]及[[2011年西班牙大奖赛|西班牙]]取得第4及第2名的成績。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9479645.stm|title=Red Bull's Sebastian Vettel clinches Turkish Grand Prix|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-05-08|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106183654/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9479645.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/13491409|title=Vettel holds off Hamilton to win Spanish Grand Prix|first=Andrew|last=Benson|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-05-22|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2015-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227110408/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/13491409|dead-url=no}}</ref>

