到了{{F1 GP|2011|加拿大}}，漢米爾頓於一號彎與韋伯擦撞，重回賽道時位居其隊友之後。幾圈後，漢米爾頓嘗試超越隊友巴頓未果，反而造成他的車輛傳動軸受損，最終僅能以退賽收場。賽後，雙方皆認為這只是一起無可厚非的比賽事故。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9511066.stm|title=Jenson Button wins stunning Canadian Grand Prix|first=Andrew|last=Benson|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-06-12|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2012-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309025751/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9511066.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>漢米爾頓在[[2011年欧洲大奖赛|瓦倫西亞]]與[[2011年英國大獎賽|銀石]]分別遭遇輪胎快速惡化及燃油不足的狀況，但是他在這兩站皆壓制著馬薩取得第4名。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9522979.stm|title=Sebastian Vettel beats Fernando Alonso in European GP|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-06-26|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2012-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313085421/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9522979.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/14099304|title=Fernando Alonso storms to Silverstone win|first=Andrew|last=Benson|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-07-10|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2015-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150302151646/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/14099304|dead-url=no}}</ref>漢米爾頓在[[2011年德国大奖赛|德國]]取得本季第二座分站冠軍。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9547042.stm|title=Lewis Hamilton wins thrilling German Grand Prix|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-07-24|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2012-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307221754/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9547042.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>漢米爾頓在[[2011年匈牙利大奖赛|匈牙利]]執行了五次進站，又因為迫使[[保罗·迪·雷斯塔|保罗·迪·雷斯塔]]駛離賽道被判罰限速通過維修道，最終以第4名完賽。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9552843.stm|title=Jenson Button beats Sebastian Vettel in Hungary|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2011-07-31|accessdate=2011-10-15|first=Sarah|last=Holt|archive-date=2012-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307043640/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9552843.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在[[2011年意大利大奖赛|蒙扎]]經過一場與麥可·舒馬克激烈的較勁後取得第4名，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9587511.stm|title=Sebastian Vettel cruises to dominant Italian GP victory|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-09-11|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2020-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200124013912/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9587511.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>賽後，漢米爾頓表示不怪罪舒馬克激進的比賽策略。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/14872901|title=Lewis Hamilton refuses to criticise Schumacher tactics|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-09-11|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2012-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015164148/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/14872901|dead-url=no}}</ref>

到了{{F1 GP|2011|新加坡}}，漢米爾頓與馬薩發生事故，致使漢米爾頓進站更換前鼻翼，並獲判限速行駛維修道一次。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9599813.stm|title=Sebastian Vettel wins in Singapore but title must wait|first=Andrew|last=Benson|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-09-25|accessdate=2012-11-20}}</ref>賽後訪談期間，漢米爾頓遭馬薩批評「開車不用大腦」。當兩人同時受訪時，馬薩抓住漢米爾頓的肩膀表示「兄弟，幹的好。」漢米爾頓則要巴西人離他遠一點。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15052980|title=Felipe Massa criticises Lewis Hamilton's driving in Singapore|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-09-25|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2013-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215063639/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15052980|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[2011年日本大獎賽|日本大獎賽]]前，漢米爾頓堅稱他在本季並未犯下任何錯誤。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15198820|title=Lewis Hamilton says he is not doing anything wrong|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-10-06|accessdate=2012-11-20}}</ref>他在正賽中遭遇輪胎爆胎，隨後又再度與馬薩碰撞；雖然法拉利要求賽會對漢米爾頓開罰，不過，最終漢米爾頓並未受罰並以第5名完賽。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9611193.stm|title=Sebastian Vettel takes crown despite Jenson Button win in Japan|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-10-09|accessdate=2012-11-20}}</ref>漢米爾頓事後希望馬薩從中成長，並認為他自己的一級方程式賽車生涯已如臨深淵。<ref>{{cite news|title=Felipe Massa must grow up|url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/motorsport/3870992/Lewis-Hamilton-Felipe-Massa-must-grow-up.html|first=Ian|last=Gordon|work=The Sun|date=2011-10-14|accessdate=2011-10-15|location=London|archive-date=2014-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009080426/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/motorsport/3870992/Lewis-Hamilton-Felipe-Massa-must-grow-up.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

漢米爾頓在[[2011年韩国大奖赛|韓國]]取得桿位，終結了紅牛的連續16座桿位紀錄。<ref>{{cite news|title=Lewis Hamilton blasts to pole at Korean Grand Prix|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/formula_one/15319152.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2011-10-15|accessdate=2011-10-15|first=Sarah|last=Holt}}</ref>正賽起跑後，他的領先地位僅保持到第4號彎，隨後便被維泰爾超越，最終漢米爾頓敗給對方，站上頒獎台第2位。<ref>{{cite news|title=Sebastien Vettel wins Korean Grand Prix from Lewis Hamilton|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/formula_one/15326210.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2011-10-16|accessdate=2011-10-23|first=Sarah|last=Holt}}</ref>到了首屆[[2011年印度大奖赛|印度大獎賽]]，漢米爾頓於排位賽中取得第二快的成績，但因為在週五自由練習賽時忽視黃旗，被判罰退三位。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15504672|title=Sebastian Vettel takes Indian Grand Prix pole|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-10-29|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2014-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724125920/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15504672|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15489950|title=Hamilton given Indian Grand Prix grid penalty|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-10-28|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2014-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724165855/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15489950|dead-url=no}}</ref>漢米爾頓從第5位起跑後，比賽過程中又再次與馬薩發生碰撞，致使漢米爾頓進站更換鼻翼，馬薩則遭判罰。最終，漢米爾頓在本站以第7名完賽。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9627687.stm|title=Sebastian Vettel wins inaugural Indian Grand Prix|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-10-30|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2019-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190618022347/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9627687.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>漢米爾頓於[[2011年阿布扎比大奖赛|阿布達比]]從第2位起跑贏得分站冠軍。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9638444.stm|title=Lewis Hamilton wins Abu Dhabi GP battle with Fernando Alonso|first=Sarah|last=Holt|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-11-13|accessdate=2012-11-20|archive-date=2012-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313133645/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9638444.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>漢米爾頓在[[2011年巴西大獎賽|巴西]]因變速箱故障以退賽收場，年度積分榜名列第5。他在本站與馬薩達成和解，為雙方本季的戰火劃下句點。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15913466|title=Lewis Hamilton finally ends feud with Felipe Massa|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-11-27|accessdate=2012-11-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9649301.stm|title=Mark Webber beats Sebastian Vettel to win season-ending Brazilian GP|first=Andrew|last=Benson|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]|date=2011-11-27|accessdate=2012-11-20}}</ref>

